incident_description: Highest category incident, requires immediate attention and resolution within 12 hours
Major incident, requires urgent attention and resolution after 24 hours
Serious incident, but does not incurr financial or external dammage. Requires triage within 4 hours and resolution after 48 hours
Minor incident, requires triage within 4 hours and resolution after 1 week
Low level incident, observation or query. Triage within 8 hours and resolution after 1 month
